C.CRGA1||'GST',C.CRGA1) ) AND VW_OUT_PAYMENT_DETAIL.PROCESSING_UNIT = '$$STR_PROCESSING_UNIT' AND IN_ETL_CONTROL.TXT_KEY_STRING = '$$STR_MAX_CYCLE_DATE' AND IN_ETL_CONTROL.TXT_FILE_NAME = 9999) IN (9999, 0, 2) AND VW_OUT_PAYMENT_DETAIL.POSTPIPELINERUNSEQ NOT IN (SELECT dec_postpipelinerunseq FROM out_cycle_postedpipeline_trace)) OR (NVL(IN_ETL_CONTROL.DEC_ENFORCE_FLG, 9999) IN (1) AND VW_OUT_PAYMENT_DETAIL.POSTPIPELINERUNSEQ IN (SELECT T.Dec_Postpipelinerunseq FROM out_cycle_postedpipeline_trace T WHERE 1 = 1 --AND VW_OUT_PAYMENT_DETAIL.POSTPIPELINERUNSEQ =T.Dec_Postpipelinerunseq AND VW_OUT_PAYMENT_DETAIL.PROCESSING_UNIT = T.TXT_PROCESSING_UNIT AND VW_OUT_PAYMENT_DETAIL.CYCLE_TYPE = T.TXT_CYCLE_TYPE AND VW_OUT_PAYMENT_DETAIL.CYCLE_DATE = T.DTE_CYCLE_DATE)))

TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: update out_payment_detail a set a.txt_remarks = (select max(txt_Remarks) from in_tblBank_account act where substr(a.txt_position_name,4,5) = act.txtagy_no and act.txtcurrency=A.txt_payment_currency AND a.txt_processing_unit='PD_PU' -- and a.txt_business_unit='SGPPD' group by TXTAGY_NO ) where exists (select 1 from in_tblBank_account act where act.txt_Remarks is not null and txtcomp_no='011' and act.txtcurrency=A.txt_payment_currency AND a.txt_processing_unit='PD_PU' -- and a.txt_business_unit='SGPPD' and a.dte_cycle_date = (select to_date(c.txt_key_value, 'yyyy-mm-dd')from IN_ETL_CONTROL c where c.TXT_KEY_STRING = 'OPER_CYCLE_DATE' AND c.TXT_FILE_NAME = 'GLOBAL') and a.txt_cycle_type = (select d.txt_key_value from IN_ETL_CONTROL d where d.TXT_KEY_STRING = 'PAYMENT_CYCLE_TYPE' AND d.TXT_FILE_NAME = 'PD_PU') and substr(a.txt_position_name,4,5) = act.txtagy_no ); commit;
